1
00:00:36,832 --> 00:00:42,655
Varje sju sekunder.

2
00:00:42,676 --> 00:00:47,219
Varje sju sekunder mörker någon av tuberkulosen.

3
00:00:51,201 --> 00:00:55,042
I det här landet mörker tuberkulosen flera tusen människor varje år.

4
00:00:57,045 --> 00:01:02,747
I hela världen mörker mer än 4 miljoner människor varje år av tuberkulosen.

5
00:01:10,588 --> 00:01:11,930
This is Maria.

6
00:01:12,911 --> 00:01:14,251
She might be someone you know.

7
00:01:15,212 --> 00:01:17,132
Will she be attacked by tuberculosis?

8
00:01:18,635 --> 00:01:21,436
Will she be alive a few years from now?

9
00:01:24,457 --> 00:01:26,239
Let us see what her chances are.

10
00:01:30,162 --> 00:01:33,745
Let us suppose that the inside of Maria's lungs looks like this.

11
00:01:37,204 --> 00:01:41,649
Och låt oss tänka oss att germen som skapar tuberculosis ser ut så här ut.

12
00:01:41,668 --> 00:01:49,855
När de här germen attackerar Maria så skapar hennes kropp naturliga vapen för att kämpa mot dem.

13
00:02:31,687 --> 00:02:34,549
If the defense is strong enough, the enemy is defeated.

14
00:02:34,588 --> 00:02:40,413
The defenders remain in Marias body to protect her against future attacks of tuberculosis.

15
00:02:48,638 --> 00:02:50,879
And Maria remains well and happy.

16
00:02:54,981 --> 00:02:58,645
But sometimes the attack of tuberculosis is too strong.

17
00:03:00,609 --> 00:03:02,330
Sometimes the defense is too weak.

18
00:03:02,349 --> 00:03:02,991
Then tuberculosis wins.

19
00:03:33,884 --> 00:03:36,225
Det här är männen av tuberkulosis.

20
00:03:36,706 --> 00:03:39,908
Tusen barn och äldre som är seriöst sjuka.

21
00:03:39,929 --> 00:03:43,371
Tusen som kan dö av tuberkulosis.

22
00:03:43,390 --> 00:03:47,473
Ska Maria bli nästa?

23
00:03:48,453 --> 00:03:50,133
Kan något göras för att skydda henne?

24
00:03:51,055 --> 00:03:54,236
Ja, Maria kan skyddas av vaccination.

25
00:04:01,669 --> 00:04:05,492
Vaccination can give Maria's body the defense she needs against tuberculosis.

26
00:04:05,733 --> 00:04:18,103
And then tuberculosis will lose the battle.

27
00:04:24,208 --> 00:04:30,093
Today, in our country and in many other countries, tuberculosis has many allies.

28
00:04:31,851 --> 00:04:40,800
Städer i ruiner, förstörda sjukhus, tråk, djur, dåligt byggnad, sjukdom.

29
00:04:40,819 --> 00:04:48,846
Männen i världen har samlat sig med oss för att kämpa mot tuberkulosis.

30
00:04:49,752 --> 00:05:04,185
Vår ministerie för sjukvård leder kriget här med hjälp av UNICEF, United Nations International Children's Emergency Fund, World Health Organization, Red Cross och relieforganisationer från Danmark, Norge och Sverige.

31
00:05:06,247 --> 00:05:09,610
Alla är tillsammans i den internationella tuberkulosen-kampanjen.

32
00:05:11,291 --> 00:05:15,675
International cooperation against the international enemy, tuberculosis.

33
00:05:20,009 --> 00:05:21,011
We must act quickly.

34
00:05:21,711 --> 00:05:22,932
The enemy is on the march.

35
00:05:24,072 --> 00:05:27,014
Every seven seconds tuberculosis kills a human being.

36
00:05:28,035 --> 00:05:30,536
Every seven seconds.

37
00:05:30,576 --> 00:05:31,576
We must act quickly.

38
00:05:32,557 --> 00:05:37,480
Our scientists and laboratories and men of many lands are forging the weapons to protect us.

39
00:06:35,668 --> 00:06:37,629
War is declared on tuberculosis.

40
00:06:37,649 --> 00:06:43,194
Our forces are mobilized.

41
00:06:44,055 --> 00:06:46,456
Our counterattack rolls forth.

42
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:53,701
Motorized forces.

43
00:06:59,605 --> 00:07:00,687
Supported from the air.

44
00:07:05,512 --> 00:07:06,173
En varg.

45
00:07:11,341 --> 00:07:13,463
Defensive av life against death.

46
00:07:44,399 --> 00:07:48,661
Vård mot tuberkulosa är pågående runt om i vårt land och i många andra länder.

47
00:07:49,461 --> 00:07:51,622
Vaccination för alla som behövs.

48
00:08:11,634 --> 00:08:12,115
I land.

49
00:08:12,136 --> 00:08:12,295
I water.

50
00:08:12,315 --> 00:08:12,716
And by air.

51
00:08:12,735 --> 00:08:14,257
Defensive of life against protection familiar.

52
00:08:41,433 --> 00:08:43,014
A lifebelt for your daughter.

53
00:08:43,054 --> 00:08:46,176
New protection for your son.

54
00:08:46,216 --> 00:08:47,096
New hope for Maria.

55
00:09:13,519 --> 00:09:16,000
Men vår främling har allier.

56
00:09:18,602 --> 00:09:26,028
Folk som sprider falska berättelser om vaccineringen.

57
00:09:26,109 --> 00:09:27,029
Och folk som lyssnar på dem.

58
00:09:27,049 --> 00:09:28,610
Som Marias mor.

59
00:09:28,630 --> 00:09:33,433
Var inte orolig.

60
00:09:33,474 --> 00:09:36,096
Missa inte chansen att skydda dina barn från tuberkulosis.

61
00:09:36,116 --> 00:09:37,116
Många har varit vaccinerade.

62
00:09:41,738 --> 00:09:45,879
In this country, thousands of people have already received this protection.

63
00:09:45,899 --> 00:09:52,923
Not one person has ever been hurt by this vaccination.

64
00:09:52,942 --> 00:09:57,485
Millions of lives can be saved.

65
00:09:57,585 --> 00:09:59,426
One chance less for tuberculosis.

66
00:10:00,447 --> 00:10:02,847
One chance more for your child.
